&lt;DIV&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;&lt;FONT color=#6633ff&gt;As a shadowknight with about 700 AAs, I have NO trouble tanking regular group content less perhaps 10% of the regular group content mobs.&amp;nbsp; Again, this is reasonable, if I wanted to tank EVERY group content mob out there I would have rolled a war.&lt;/FONT&gt;&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;What is on the lips of many players of the game, is giving a lesser form of defensive to knights, so that they may be given an improved ability to tank mobs that are balanced for warriors with defensive. &lt;FONT color=#cc00cc&gt;&lt;FONT color=#6633ff&gt;(We currently have this, gimped, as it should be)&lt;/FONT&gt;&amp;nbsp; &lt;/FONT&gt;I feel that that is the wrong approach. I believe that for the health of the game and for the ultimate happiness of the players, it's time to get rid of defensive and evasive in its entirely. These problems are just going to keep occurring over and over again until the problem is fixed.&amp;nbsp; &lt;FONT color=#6633ff&gt;These "problems" are game design, and again, are meant to be there.&amp;nbsp; &lt;/FONT&gt;&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
