&lt;DIV&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;&lt;FONT color=#6633ff&gt;The knights gimped Defensive gave us a slight edge that allowed us to tank perhaps another one percent of the mobs that we previously could not.&amp;nbsp; As a knight I am at the tanking level I should be.&amp;nbsp; Nothing is broken.&amp;nbsp; Nothing needs fixing.&amp;nbsp; War Defensive and Evasive is as it should be.&lt;/FONT&gt;&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
